title: ‘Ozark’ Season 4 Part 1, Episodes 5-7
description:
Joanna and Van return give their thoughts on episodes 5 through 7 of the fourth and final season of ‘Ozark.' They also discuss where they would like to see the show go in its final episodes.
Hosts: Joanna Robinson and Van Lathan
Producer: Steve Ahlman
